The paper presents a software package for simulating and training recurrent neural networks using biologically-realistic models and learning algorithms. This work is relevant to several sub-fields of computer science, including neural networks (cs.NE), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), systems and control (cs.SY), and computer vision (cs.CV).
